@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kelgus(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v0
    v1 = v2
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.34) + v1)
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v0 + 0.69 * v1 + 0.18)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v0 + 0.16 * v0 + 0.72)))
    v0 = (0.74 / (0.19 / (tmp + 0.55 - v0 + 0.46)))
    data[tid] = v0
